  <text>
     <body>
     <div type="encomium">
   <pb facs="9"/>
   <l>
      <hi>GErard</hi> of late was but in Latine read,</l>
   <l>But now he hath his language altered:</l>
   <l>Behold a change! see how Arts pencill can</l>
   <l>A <hi>Latine</hi> turn into an <hi>English-man.</hi>
   </l>
   <l>
      <hi>Gerard</hi> in this ten thousand doth excell,</l>
   <l>In three moneths space to speak our tongue so well.</l>
   <closer>
      <signed>Thomas Bonham.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
